{"tid":585065,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【七警上訴】律政司指認人程序公正","createTime":"2018-03-08T10:22:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T13:02:44.000Z","uid":150685,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a1cf687d97cdaf25efa9fe2eade8f6217f6c2f0e","tid":585065,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T10:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180308/large/1520493411_e6b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180308%2Flarge%2F1520493411_e6b6.jpg&h=489a7e78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180308/large/1520490298_d342.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180308%2Flarge%2F1520490298_d342.jpg&h=55c12824&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n七警於傘運期間在金鐘添馬公園暗角毆打曾健超被判監兩年，其中四警早前已獲上訴庭批出上訴許可。法庭今早處理餘下三警的申請，<span style=\"color: red;\">其中警長白榮斌當日穿著「醒目」灰色粉紅色間條有領上衣，被原審法官認出。惟上訴方今指「目測」可見白的上衣灰間較粗，比例為「1：3.5」，可是涉打人的行兇者上衣灰間闊度相若</span>。惟上訴庭法官坦言看不到，而且這些論點在原審時根本沒有人提出。<br />\n<br />\n代表白榮斌的資深大律師質疑抬走曾健超的人，在鏡頭拍不到的49秒已經換了人。上訴方指白當天的上衣在粉紅間條中有一條紅線，然而在打人片段，看不到紅線。法官看著手上的相片，坦言看不到所謂紅線，遑論要在片段看到。<br />\n法官又指，以上論點在原審時沒有提出，法官在考慮證供自然沒有考慮，上訴庭沒有權力重審再認人。<br />\n<br />\n至於第五被告陳少丹的代表資深大狀則指，認人程序有不當地方，而原審法官錯誤接納該些認人證供。上訴方指曾健超可能在認人前已經看過大量關於七警的資料；而認人行列只有一人，而不是一般將被告混在戲子之中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180308/57919464\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180308%2F57919464&d=E3fy1ovkgYbkuPBlE3JVixxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=f5167bca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180308%2F57919464&h=07713b15\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180308/57919464</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都up得出，要幾眼盲先可以睇到唔係同一個人？<br />\n仲要係同一team人做野，會突然轉咗人？"},{"pid":"5ad3651f83e4d86065b8bd25f9107219904dd8b0","tid":585065,"uid":18948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:04:42.000Z","msg":"打證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f062421ffe1eee699a40400a29e5efd85e2ab6","tid":585065,"uid":35014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:18:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9e5b2fbb3320ff26d22352bdafaa09d1ff52b07","tid":585065,"uid":11809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:30:18.000Z","msg":"坐啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afae10ee0fcfc760c2b2edebca0fa2e636a1af38","tid":585065,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T12:11:33.000Z","msg":"做得律師<br />\n<br />\n就要預佐盲撐架啦<br />\n<br />\n受人錢財替人消災"},{"pid":"3d59fe2cacb066374581886454d5e6b646246344","tid":585065,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9e5b2fbb3320ff26d22352bdafaa09d1ff52b07","tid":585065,"uid":11809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:30:18.000Z","msg":"坐啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T12:16:56.000Z","msg":"阿sir死撐唔撚使你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43597c56b4a722dfc01cd4b9638b5ed48b44990e","tid":585065,"uid":55043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T12:23:29.000Z","msg":"當時申請上訴明明係申請覆刑期<br />\n<br />\n做咩搞搞下變左翻案<img src=\"/assets/fac